Class Login

java.lang.Object
  beans.Login
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Login
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class makes it able for a user to registrate. This class also sets the right for each user, employee or admin so some might be able to add something, while others cant. There is also a way to edit your own profile and there is a login screen. All information will be saved into database.
